<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>Resurections</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois.cgi?Landaen">Landaen</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 2:43 p.m. 8/6/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Resurections<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/datel.gif" width=46 height=22 border=0><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/dateblnk.gif" width=100 height=22 border=0><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/dater.gif" width=306 height=22 border=0></center><BR></STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#F4D99F FACE=arial>
<P>From what I have seen there have been no patches to help even the cleric out with other classes.

<BR>Druids are way more powerful than clerics and so of course everyone now plays druids because it is easy to level by running fast away from big monsters and letting your DOT spells kill them as you run. The only thing that a cleric gets that no other class gets is the ability to resurect the dead. BIG DEAL - now that they have cut the exp loss by 50% that spell is now 50% as powerful. and should cost less and be used at lower levels. But really what good does this spell do for the Cleric except give him a warm spot in his heart and a hearty thanks from the person he just brought back from the dead ( and maybe miles away). Why dont we get exp for resing people ??? And who is going to res me when I die ?? It has never Once ( EVER ) paid off or benifited me in any way to reserect someone !!!
<P>Im seriously thinking of stoping my cleric and playing a Druid. ( Why struggle )
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
